        "from": "T10n0279_012:0062a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸佛子！",
        "from": "T10n0279_012:0062a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如此娑婆世界中，說四聖諦，有四百億十千名。",
        "from": "T10n0279_012:0062a27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，東方百千億無數無量、無邊無等、不可數、不可稱、不可思、不可量、不可說，盡法界、虛空界、所有世界，彼一一世界中，說四聖諦，亦各有四百億十千名；隨眾生心，悉令調伏。",
        "from": "T10n0279_012:0062a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如東方，南、西、北方，四維、上、下，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T10n0279_012:0062b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛子！",
        "from": "T10n0279_012:0062b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
